Package org.kududb.mapreduce.tools

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CsvParser
    Column-separated values parser that gives access to the different columns inside each line of data.
    ImportCsv
    Map-only job that reads CSV files and inserts them into a single Kudu table.
    ImportCsvMapper
    Mapper that ingests CSV lines and turns them into Kudu Inserts.
    IntegrationTestBigLinkedList
    This is an integration test borrowed from goraci, written by Keith Turner, which is in turn inspired by the Accumulo test called continous ingest (ci).
    RowCounter
    Map-only job that counts all the rows in the provided table.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ImportCsv.Counters  
    RowCounter.Counters
    Counter enumeration to count the actual rows.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CsvParser.BadCsvLineException
    Exception used when the CsvParser is unable to parse a line.
